G1 E-2 F2700 ; retract filament
G1 Z5 F3000 ; lift nozzle 5mm
G90 ; absolute positioning
G1 X5 Y250 F6000 ; present print
M104 S0 ; turn off hotend
M140 S0 ; turn off bed
M107 ; turn off fan
M84 ; disable steppers
